#1503
Vampire: A Legacy in Crimson~
   You exchange pleasantries with the vampire and share your condolences over
being trapped in the tiny store room during the day.
   'If only I hadn't lost my minion', the vampire laments. 'What's that? You
don't have one? How will you ever establish your legacy without a minion? Here,
take this spare peeping stone. It'll help you find the perfect minion. Of
course, if you really want to be a powerful vampire, you also need to
demonstrate power over our greatest enemy: the sun. Ever caused an eclipse
yourself? I managed it once. A truly difficult ritual. But it's the only path
to greatness. That, and a good minion.'
   The vampire hands you a blood-red stone and gives you a brief description of
its use. It seems it can transform an ordinary citizen into the perfect minion.
Use it to 'peep <citizen>' until you find the right one, then type 'minionize
<citizen>' to transform them into your own personal minion!
   To cement your legacy, perform the following:
   1. Master your vampire powers,
   2. Reach level 100,
   3. Complete the Eclipse Ritual, and, most importantly,
   4. Find yourself a dark minion using the peeping stone
~
   'Yes, m'lord,' your minion says. 'Your legacy is secure.'
~
