#1504
Battle: Campaign of Triumphs~
   A city guard stops you as you pass, saying, 'Wow, I've actually heard of
you! I didn't think we had anybody famous here. Well, almost famous, anyway.
You've got to show the world how great you are. To think, our own champion
right here at home.'
   The guard rattles off a list of battles you might fight in order to show off
your might and start your own legends, from a flame dragon to a polar baron,
and plenty in-between. You realize, of course, that the guard is right.
   In fact, you resolve to defeat ALL the challenges on the list and establish
yourself amongst the legends. You'll just need to finish the Battle skill tree,
reach level 100, and defeat all of these foes:
   1. A swamp hag
   2. A flame dragon
   3. A hoarfrost serragon
   4. A loch colossus in Burrow Canyons
   5. The undead caretaker of Mill Manor
   6. An Archdruid of the Grove
   7. Furl, war shaman, in a Goblin Challenge
   8. Vanguard Leader Dryleef at a Goblin Outpost
   9. Scylla beneath the Golden Goblin
   10. The Saguaro Treant beyond a Monsoon Rift
   11. Aquilo, Polar Baron of the Permafrost
   12. The Sun King inside a Lost Temple
~
   'Wow, I can't believe it's you! I heard you beat Aquilo, Dryleef, even
Scylla! Us guards had a bet going and, just between you and me, you made me a
lot of coin,' the city guard says as you stop. 'I knew you could do it.'
   The renown of your battle prowess has spread to the corners of the empire
and, perhaps the world. Someday you might be the most famous warrior alive!
~
